# DayFi

> Send money with just a username. Multi-asset wallet on Stellar.

## Project Structure
dayfi/
├── backend/          # Node.js + Express + Prisma
│   ├── src/
│   │   ├── routes/   # auth, wallet, user, transactions
│   │   ├── services/ # walletService, emailService
│   │   └── middleware/
│   └── prisma/schema.prisma
├── lib/              # Flutter app
│   ├── providers/    # auth_provider, wallet_provider, user_provider
│   ├── screens/      # auth, home, send, receive, transactions, settings
│   ├── services/     # api_service
│   └── theme/        # app_theme
└── website/          # Landing page


## Backend Setup
```bash
cd backend
cp .env.example .env
# Fill in your values (DB, JWT, Stellar, email)

npm install
npx prisma migrate dev --name init
npm run dev
```

### Required env vars

| Key | Description |
|-----|-------------|
| DATABASE_URL | PostgreSQL connection string |
| JWT_SECRET | 64-char random hex |
| WALLET_ENCRYPTION_KEY | 64-char hex (32 bytes) |
| STELLAR_NETWORK | testnet or mainnet |
| USDC_ISSUER | USDC issuer address |
| RESEND_API_KEY | From resend.com |

Generate secrets:
```bash
node -e "console.log(require('crypto').randomBytes(64).toString('hex'))"
```

## Flutter App Setup
```bash
flutter pub get
flutter run
```

### Firebase Setup (Push Notifications)
1. Create Firebase project at console.firebase.google.com
2. Add iOS + Android apps
3. Download `google-services.json` → `android/app/`
4. Download `GoogleService-Info.plist` → `ios/Runner/`

### Biometrics (iOS)
Add to `ios/Runner/Info.plist`:
```xml
<key>NSFaceIDUsageDescription</key>
<string>Use Face ID to sign in to DayFi</string>
```

### Android Biometrics
Add to `android/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml`:
```xml
<uses-permission android:name="android.permission.USE_BIOMETRIC"/>
```

## Docker Deployment
```bash
cp backend/.env.example backend/.env
# Fill in values

docker compose up -d
```

Services:
- Backend API: http://localhost:3001
- Website: http://localhost:80
- Postgres: localhost:5432

## API Endpoints

### Auth
| Method | Path | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| POST | /api/auth/send-otp | Send OTP to email |
| POST | /api/auth/verify-otp | Verify OTP, get token |
| POST | /api/auth/setup-username | Set @dayfi.me username |
| GET  | /api/auth/check-username/:u | Check availability |

### Wallet
| Method | Path | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| GET | /api/wallet/balance | Get balances (USDC, XLM, GOLD, BTC) |
| POST | /api/wallet/send | Send any supported asset |
| POST | /api/wallet/swap | Swap between assets |
| GET | /api/wallet/address | Get wallet address + QR data |
| GET | /api/wallet/resolve/:id | Resolve username or address |

### Transactions
| Method | Path | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| GET | /api/transactions | Paginated history |
| GET | /api/transactions/:id | Single transaction |

